headline: Senate Republicans cannot force US Postal Service to scrap EVs, parliamentarian says
summary: WASHINGTON -Senate Republicans cannot force the U.S. Postal Service to scrap thousands of electric vehicles and charging equipment in a massive tax and budget bill, the Senate parliamentarian said...
